Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, have you picked a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem pretty athletic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try tennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for me, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, Aoi, everyone's trying to recruit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the enrollment season.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking of joining, Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it into college,\Nso I'd like to try something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Aoi is so cool.\N- The bus won't be here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something about\Nthat folding bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long Riders!\NEpisode 1  A Small Miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you\Nto be interested in cycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ride a bike like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I could manage\Nthat one we just saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You on a bike makes me nervous, Ami.\NI think you'd fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tripped just now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But you know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've sorta been curious\Nabout cycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really?\N- Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you ride your bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to really enjoy it...\Nlike it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was afraid of falling,\Nlike you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I couldn't make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I can give it a go\Non a cute bicycle like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared of falling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can manage that bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a shop that\Nmight carry one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they sell them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's small and cute,\Nand so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have all kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the prices are unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The extra digit's a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, for models like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prices aren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one's over 600,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one over there is\Nclose to a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can bikes cost so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I withdrew all my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My entire savings of\N62,052 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even make a dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew a bicycle is so expensive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this shop's not that expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as far as performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bike is small,\Nbut solid..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll bet it's expensive\Nand out of my reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not cheap...\Nbut cheaper than the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference from\Nthe other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so there's efficiency\Nand performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I admit, it's cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a look\Nat others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to ride a bike.\NSo what's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to\Nride the bike to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I haven't given it\Na thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was never good at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I want this to be\Na long-term commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Riding on this bike and moving\Nmy body seems like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can continue,\NI think it'll give me confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I...might be able to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we go cycling\Nduring our free day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll give you a reason to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cycling with him... Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going! I'm definitely going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely! Definitely! De-fi-nitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, okay, Aoi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What great things\Nare in store for you and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are sooo cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be together\Nfrom now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect day for cycling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pontakun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is shining on you\Nand you sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. I was so excited last night,\NI didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bike is really cool though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...my Pontakun is just as cute\Nas yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pontakun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pontiankh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, Pontiankh... a.k.a. Pontakun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Short, sweet and cute!\NIsn't it the perfect name for this bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to calm down\N'cuz it can be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could ride\Non this bike path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have to worry\Nabout cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's an easy path,\Nabout 40 kilos round trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just right for\Na beginner like you, Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get tired,\Nwe don't have to go all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play it by ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shall we go, Pontakun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so neat the way\Nthe scenery passes by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world seems higher\Nthan usual
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everything I'm used to seeing\Nlooks brand new to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class B River\NSakai River\NKanagawa Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we've ridden so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away and\Ngo too fast. You'll get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I could\Ngo on forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel energy pushing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know how it feels,\NI can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands and legs are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly I didn't have strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I could go anywhere\Non this bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suddenly didn't have strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, did you eat a proper breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd feel sick\Nif I ate before exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to eat properly!\NNo wonder you collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before any exercise, you need\Ngood rest and nutrition. That's basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lack of sleep and\Nno breakfast before exercising...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you got hit by hunger knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hunger knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, you ran out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to replenish\Nyour energy to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think we'd need\Nsupplements at this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend got hunger knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is she a beginner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, today's my first time cycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A food supplement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this and rest a bit,\Nthen you'll be able to pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't taste great,\Nbut it works fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat is all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sorta leaves an aftertaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing! I feel stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should get\Na little more nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good place for that nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel revitalized!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a dairy farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there was a place\Nlike this around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the smallest dairy farm in Japan.\NPeople probably don't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cycling without eating?\NNo wonder you hit the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing\Nit happened near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're exhausted from cycling,\Nnothing beats their gelato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could eat this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come every day then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means cycling here every day though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you have to replenish\Nyour energy along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should put this on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh!\N- What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to ask their names.\NThey were so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met while cycling.\NI'm sure we'll see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Aoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize after cycling today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy riding a bike, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caused you and those two\Nso much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Riding my bike with you\Nwas sooo much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go cycling again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. But next time,\Ndon't get hunger knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll eat and get lots of sleep\Nfor the next time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shall we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We have to go back\Non the same path!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pooped, Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it slow and hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really strained your muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't move 'cuz you're hungry,\Nwant this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I had...yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with this little gem of a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my cycling life began!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first experience with cycling\Nwas so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery I passed, the gelato at\Nthe finish line... How awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Long Riders:\N"Cycling on the Beach!"
